(10, 'en_us', 'Diamond Events appear in search results above Gold and Silver Events. \r\nContains Summary View and Detail view. \r\nTitle, Date, Time, Logo Image, Address, Summary Description, Driving Directions, Phone, Web Link, E-mail, Contact Name, Photo Gallery, Detail Description, E-mail to Friend, Add to Favorites, Print, Facebook Like and Send button, Google +1 button, Recurring option.', 'default'),
